PARAM_CHUNK_ANNOTATION_CLASS

public static final String PARAM_CHUNK_ANNOTATION_CLASS
"ChunkAnnotationClass" is a single, required, string parameter that names the class of the type system chunk annotation type. An example value might be something like:
org.cleartk.type.ne.NamedEntityMention
